adultAltar.hintText: An awakening voice from the&Sacred Realm will call those&destined to be Sages, who dwell&in the %rfive temples%w.^$8%yWater Temple%w...^$3%gDeku Tree%w...^$4%rDodongo's Cavern%w...^$5%bShadow Temple%w...^$6%yJabu-Jabu's Belly%w...^$7%pFire Temple%w...^$lThe awakened ones will await for&the Hero to find %gGreg%w.^$bAnd the %revil one%w's key will be&provided by Zelda once %r5&Spiritual Stones and Medallions%w&are retrieved.^$kTogether with the Hero of Time,&the awakened ones will return&the light of peace to the world...

ganonHintText: Ha ha ha... You'll never beat me by&reflecting my lightning bolts and&unleashing the arrows from %rShadow&Temple%w!^And even if you do, you'll never&find the legendary blade hidden in&%rJabu-Jabu's Belly%w!
dampeText: Whoever reads this, please enter&%rForest Temple%w. I will let you have&my stretching, shrinking keepsake.^I'm waiting for you.&--Dampé
